&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://qstatic.zuimeia.com/img/article/6171/969b4bf08f8566a0e6f67bb4cde9cee7_720x720.jpg?imageMogr/v2/gravity/South/crop/!720x720-0-0&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;200&quot; height=&quot;200&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
